WEBVTT

00:08:28.270 --> 00:08:31.608
that everyone whom you
will meet on this day

00:08:31.632 --> 00:08:33.889
will be blessed by you,

00:08:35.599 --> 00:08:37.328
just by your eyes,

00:08:39.048 --> 00:08:40.660
by your smile,

00:08:42.835 --> 00:08:44.255
by your touch,

00:08:46.153 --> 00:08:48.086
just by your presence.

00:08:50.517 --> 00:08:54.061
Let the gratefulness overflow

00:08:54.085 --> 00:08:56.623
into blessing all around you.

00:08:57.401 --> 00:08:59.401
(Music)